Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've really betrayed Fairy Tail, \Nthen you must have some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:24.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothin' like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:01.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:07.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now all my research has come to \Nfruition, and I have completed my Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you people be singing \Nmy praises or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the voice of this Daphne person?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us Natsu back this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but no can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you realize that my Dragonoid here \Nmoves by sucking out Natsu Dragneel's magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sucking out my magic power?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship will overcome the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I've sucked out all that magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't givin' Natsu Dragneel back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To a wizard, one's magic \Npower is their very life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give back Natsu now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:04.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep up the good work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be fully charged in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:11.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, my Dragonoid will be \Noperational for half an eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get in her way? Just try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:19.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although even with your powers combined,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I highly doubt you can hold out long \Nenough to see it fully charged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:24.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:32.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of a dangerous, dragon-crazed wizard \Nwho was trying to create an artificial dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such slanderous rumors... \NSo far from the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:44.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They should say "the genius scientist Daphne \Nsucceeded in creating an artificial dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:47.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Artificial dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The egg remains I found back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was truly a long struggle \Nfor me to perfect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started with the first step: \NSuccessfully hatching an artificial dragon from an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:14.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city I lived in was the perfect \Nplace to gather data, or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:19.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the people who come from my \Ncity can all use Hidden, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:24.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to experiment on the \Ncity, I had no more use for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:30.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes! If you like playing \Nhide-and-go-seek so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...hide for the rest of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:42.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment, I made it so they \Ncould not dispel their Hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I also punished the incomplete \Ndragons who were unable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to sense the people who had \Nvanished with their Hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:05.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then? When I went to that city...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Igneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:10.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I left the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:22.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Igneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:29.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, it became known \Nas the "City without Sound".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:36.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I continued my research, and \Nfinally it dawned on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed the power of a Dragon \NSlayer to activate the Dragonoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes, Natsu Dragneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep working until you drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For me, and my evil ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:04.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's not just big, it's \Nalso gonna be seriously tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:12.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do \Nby creating such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My great ambition is to complete \Nthe perfect Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this is nothing more than a prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:25.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First up, we have to test \Nits current ability! Test!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:30.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower half's mobility is \Nsub-par, I see. Yes-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking is impossible, say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's trouble! She's really big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I know! She's what they \Ncall a "Mad Scientist"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop it somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Natsu-san inside, we \Ncan't just attack carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, does it really matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you wished for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:01.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone and done it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I am a Man, I will bring \Nyou back to the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think ill of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Master's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:21.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Looks like he got word of Daphne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:26.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's decided to ask Gray how \Nto get rid of that giant thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Don't tell me... It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying? That's so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you can complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... It's heading straight for Magnolia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:57.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late for \Nanyone to stop my Dragonoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy and the rest of you return to \Nthe guild and get everyone mobilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect Magnolia, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what would happen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop that Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray... What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do all that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You deal with Gray, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:38.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you take care of Natsu, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your word as a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:41.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is "Lizardman".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:00.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An artificial creature that \Nmimics people's attributes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:07.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you have the same attributes \Nas I, you don't carry the same burdens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes... Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:21.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made sure to take careful records \Nof the previous battle's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon find out the \Npower of my Lizardmen v. 2.5!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Titania... Erza Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. These are the spiky \Nfellows Erza talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Came to take Gray back, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks more like they're \Nhere to wipe us all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man will repel the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:01.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic! Take shelter in Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:13.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Dragon-thing \Nthat Lucy mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city's gonna be destroyed at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't guarantee that the \Nguild will be safe, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:20.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the master know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:23.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to gather everyone from the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:27.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The bunch that went to capture \NGray ain't come back either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:30.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a hard head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beast Arm... Iron Bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:46.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Smoke Fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I've lost my touch... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wakaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gettin' him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:32.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all... Were you really working \Nwith them behind the scenes, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:37.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saved by Natsu countless times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I screwed up on a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he was a kid, \Nhe had a smart mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and never thought about \Nconsequences to his actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:53.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For shame, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Man, what matters is \Nhow he takes responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll see to it that Gray \Ntakes responsibility for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Over: Beast Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful city.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting chills up my spine just thinking \Nabout how fun it'll be to pulverize it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So sit there in your box seat \Nand watch the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming you even have the \Nstrength to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Natsu, the Dragon Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I've heard it somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:10.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The pot's talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the people who live in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:24.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of a magic called Hidden, \Nyou can't see our bodies anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then just undo the magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:32.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We called out to you \Nbecause we can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:39.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Fairy Tail Wizard! I'm \Nthe Dragon Slayer, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:43.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A Dragon Slayer? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't have to be {\i1}that{\i0} surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Natsu, the Dragon Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, rid us of this magic curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like destroy the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. You must defeat the \None who controls dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you blabbing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can control a dragon! Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:13.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if there is someone \Nlike that, I'll beat 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:23.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will place our hopes with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:28.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will always be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a dream or something, \Nso I'd completely forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeat the one who controls dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... So this is what they meant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I promised, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Dragneel's power's \Ngrown higher than my data!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:03.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, my Dragonoid \Nwill go into overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:07.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:12.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this, if I \Ncalmly and meticulously
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,keep sucking up your magic at \Na reasonable pace, then AOK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes-yes, excellent work. Thank \Nyou for the lovely magic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:41.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got trouble! Elfman and \Nthe others came back, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Wakaba and Macao to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan... Take it from here... Save Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:03.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:11.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have brought you with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop bawling all over yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:22.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep moping around like that forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that ain't gonna make Lisanna smile, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always smiling, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was smiling until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's the way \Nshe was! That's Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sad times when she smiled even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:51.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what they call being a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Leave Natsu to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal him with my Sky Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Wendy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You awake, Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what the hell's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:23.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:28.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way that Gray-sama \Nhas betrayed Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia believes in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what people say... Even if \Nthe whole world turned against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're takin' me to Gramps, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we have time to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're making sure you \Ndon't try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:52.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:58.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:00.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:03.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay... I have to cure Wakaba-san \Nand Macao-san soon, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! If you use any more Sky \NMagic, your own life will be at risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you should!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can really be a member of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:28.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you're so stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:36.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please work \Ntogether and save Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We all owe Natsu, big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:44.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. When we were beat up by Phantom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:48.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu fought for us back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu gave me courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for everyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:56.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, we'll be the ones to save Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:19:00.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! If we all work \Ntogether, we can save Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:09.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:14.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail is a guild that \Nlives and dies with Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first priority is to protect \Nthe city from being destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want us to attack that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Natsu is inside of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As Master of Fairy Tail, I order you all:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:31.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Use any means necessary \Nto stop the Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? He'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His body's built nice and sturdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:44.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:52.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not a wizard that would \Nbe done in by something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:01.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:04.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We communicated by fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have already thrown away my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot lose you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I am going to bring you back with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Daphne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stomp you flat, Erza Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stinger Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:22.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's started...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:25.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, tell me why!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:42.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps... Only Natsu can \Ndefeat that Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:48.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the master decided that destroying \Nthe Dragonoid was the top priority?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was sturdily \Nbuilt, so he should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:21:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:22:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On Master's orders, we will stop the \NDragonoid with our full strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we do that, I want to check with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll let you hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:12.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cock an ear and listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:22.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bust this thing up, and me along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:24:00.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far away, \Nwe'll come when you call!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's searching for \Nmonsters or defeating monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret requests? Leave them to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:09.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the problem, \Nwe'll solve it with one punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:15.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Fairy Tail in a nutshell!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Fairy Tail Wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.61,0:24:19.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think we should cut out your \Nlines, Natsu. They get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.02,0:24:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I say something wrong?
